{"tid":1057925,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"奇男揮手問候途人　街坊反喊驚︰佢笑得好心寒","createTime":"2019-03-12T08:01:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-12T08:41:59.000Z","uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"42322f624a82b99bb1d524192ae87d8c9661a6b6","tid":1057925,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T08:01:58.000Z","msg":"<strong>奇男揮手問候途人 街坊反喊驚︰佢笑得好心寒</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2TLLUGo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2TLLUGo&d=%2BklfNN7Cu7rnXjHLlXUq6JFs2tgc95e9lhkBuxw3Ky4%3D&h=cdfd263d\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2TLLUGo</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190312/photo/bkn-20190312153053309-0312_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190312155758\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190312%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190312153053309-0312_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190312155758&h=3fea0cc2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n打招呼都驚？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今時今日連打招呼都有錯？屯門有男子在商場內向途人逐一打招呼，竟被人質疑圖謀不軌，更呼籲街坊小心。有網民慨嘆，原來有禮貌都是罪。<br />\n<br />\n據Facebook專頁「屯門友」的貼文指，最近有一名爆炸頭的男子經常出現在屯門一個商場內，向途人不斷「Say Hi」，令他大感驚嚇。<br />\n<br />\n有網民更指曾目擊有小朋友走近男子，家長嚇得立即抱起孩子，形容該男子迎面走向自己時，感到「幾嚇人，笑得好心寒」，呼籲大家「最好唔好搭理咁多或者望住佢」。<br />\n<br />\n貼文引起網民熱議，有人認為男子純粹打招呼，並無惡意︰「Say個Hi都驚？」、「佢都出現咗幾個月，笑容親切，我都有Say番Hi」、「有問題保安一早做嘢啦」、「大驚小怪，人哋行過都驚，你唔好出街啦」。"},{"pid":"04b8298b67189c0dd2b144ae3bacae7448029c3e","tid":1057925,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T08:03:02.000Z","msg":"鍾景輝"},{"pid":"06aea05285343e4c17455a017fb2292fde131bfa","tid":1057925,"uid":26752,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T08:05:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/c/c6/%E4%BB%96%E6%B0%B8%E9%81%A0%E5%B0%8D%E8%91%97%E4%BD%A0%E7%AC%91.gif/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/185?cb=20161227100201\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2F